$$
\begin{array}{l} 
\frac{1}{a_{n+1}}=\frac{n-a_{n}}{(n-1) a_{n}}=\frac{n}{(n-1) a_{n}}-\frac{1}{n-1} \Rightarrow \frac{1}{n a_{n+1}}=\frac{1}{(n-1) a_{n}}-\frac{1}{n(n-1)} \\
\Rightarrow \frac{1}{n a_{n+1}}-\frac{1}{n}=\frac{1}{(n-1) a_{n}}-\frac{1}{n-1} \Rightarrow \frac{1}{(n-1) a_{n}}-\frac{1}{n-1}=\frac{1}{a_{2}}-1 \\
